    "body" : "<p>Run your application in <strong>debug</strong> <em>mode</em> by clicking on </p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/2oL50.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"></p>\n\n<p>in the upper menu of Android Studio.</p>\n\n<p>In the bottom status bar, click <code>5: Debug</code> button, next to the <code>4: Run</code> button.</p>\n\n<p>Now you should select the <code>Logcat</code> console. </p>\n\n<p>In search box, you can type the <em>tag</em> of your message, and your message should appear, like in the following picture (where the tag is <code>CREATION</code>):</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/kMA4B.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"></p>\n\n<p>Check <a href=\"https://developer.android.com/tools/debugging/debugging-studio.html\" rel=\"noreferrer\">this article</a> for more information.</p>\n"
