    "body" : "<h2>Android Studio 3.0 and earlier:</h2>\n<p>If the other solutions don't work, you can always see the output in the <em><strong><a href=\"https://developer.android.com/studio/profile/monitor\" rel=\"noreferrer\">Android Monitor</a></strong></em>.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/bR6E1.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/bR6E1.png\" alt=\"android studio screen shot\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<p>Make sure to set your filter to <strong><em>Show only selected application</em></strong> or create a custom filter.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/GcerK.png\" rel=\"noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/GcerK.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\" /></a></p>\n"
