  "title" : "How to print to the console in Android Studio?",
  "body" : "<p>I just downloaded Android Studio for Linux from: \n<a href=\"http://developer.android.com/sdk/installing/studio.html\">http://developer.android.com/sdk/installing/studio.html</a></p>\n\n<p>I'm wondering how to print to the console?</p>\n\n<p>Neither <code>System.out.print(...)</code> nor <code>Log.e(...)</code> from <code>android.util.Log</code> seem to work.</p>\n"
